  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Peel and slice the papelon into 1-inch thick rounds.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and sauté for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the papelon slices to the skillet and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, until tender.",
    "Transfer the papelon slices to a baking dish.",
    "Sprinkle the savoury breadcrumbs, salt, and black pepper over the papelon.",
    "Top with the grated cheese.",
    "Bake for 15-20 minutes, until the cheese is golden brown and bubbly.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
